{"tid":1366704,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過喺極度憤怒嘅時候激發咗自己潛在嘅巨大力量","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:52:13.000Z","uid":150100,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7020d671df222aceefcfdf08189278ecee60d263","tid":1366704,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"我試過，我真係試過<br />\n之前細個有次同老母嗌完交好嬲，之後突然間感覺到啲力量係咁湧出嚟，然後啲肌肉谷住谷住咁，之後我一嘢打落塊膠版，塊膠版即刻裂咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗我應該係悟飯嗰type<br />\n一嬲就會激發出巨大潛力"},{"pid":"8ba08b176fe1177c66e868d0205cb79016e02e02","tid":1366704,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"自此之後我都會控制好自己啲情緒，費事搞出人命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc68f639cd01dfacab636ea5ca04180fdf53ca9e","tid":1366704,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b6e186c72a9abc041900ef4c12c5bd20cf4abc","tid":1366704,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"樓主?<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/TemptingPlayfulKitty-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FTemptingPlayfulKitty-size_restricted.gif&h=bc220a9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47a5a5c0d9639175845e1460e78e744e62226111","tid":1366704,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:47:31.000Z","msg":"都係因為咁，我先唔去前線<br />\n如果唔係我嬲起上嚟<br />\n啲狗至少死大半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482f503c77dace28ef994f3b21b3e9a8c3e7ed33","tid":1366704,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"黑人細路撒雅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d686a1b